Phase 3 - Data Reporting

In the third phase, there was a focus on print layouts, screen shots, attribute tables, maps, and graphs. Data reporting primarily used QGIS, but Microsoft Excel Spreadsheet was also used to capture and organise data and at the same time, create tables.
